\c 14
\s VaJudha vanorangana kuvuraya Jesu.
\p
\v 1 Zvino mazuva maviri akanga asara pakusvika kwepaseka no\add mutambo \add*wezvingwa zvisinembiriso. Vapirisita vakuru navanyori vakanga vachitsvaka mutovo wavangamubata nawo namano, kuti va\add mu\add*vuraye.
\v 2 Nokuti vakati: Zvirege kuitwa pamutambo, kuti kurege kuva nebope pakati pavanhu.
\s Jesu unozodzwa nomukadzi paBhetaniya.
\p
\v 3 Zvino wakati paBhetaniya, mumba maSimoni wamaperembudzi, agere pakudya kwakavuya mumwe mukadzi, anechinu chearibhasiteri chaive nechi zoro chenaridho chakakosha zvikuru; akaputsa chinu cearbstera, akachidurura pamusoro wake.
\v 4 Asi kwaiva nevamwe vakatsamwa mukati mavo, vakati: Kuparadza ikoko kwechizoro kwakaitirweiko?
\v 5 Nokuti chingadai chatengeswa namadhenari anopfuvura mazana matatu,* akapiwa varombo Vakamutsamwira.
\v 6 Asi Jesu wakati: Muregei. Munomutambudzireiko? Wakandiitira basa rakanaka.
\v 7 Nokuti varombo munavo nguva dzose, nguva ipi neipi yamunoda, mungavaitira zvakanaka; asi ini hamuneni nguva. dzose.
\v 8 Wakaita paakagona napo; wakagara azodzera muviri wangu kuvigwa.
\v 9 Zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwamuri: kose kose kunozoparidzirwa Evhangeri panyika dzose, zvakaitwa naye zvicharebwavo, chive chirangaridzo chake.
\s Judhasi Iskarioti unotsvaka kutengesa Jesu.
\p
\v 10 Zvino Judhasi Iskarioti, mumwe wavanegumi navaviri, wakaenda kuvairisita vakuru, kuti amuise kwavari.
\v 11 Ivo vakati vachi\add zvi\add*nzwa, vakafara, vakamuvimbisa kuti vachamupa mari. Ipapo akatsvaka mutovo waangamuisa kwavari nawo panguva yakafanira.
\s Paseka Nechirairo.
\p
\v 12 Nezuva rokutanga rezvingwa zvisinembiriso, musi wavaibaya paseka nawo, vadzidzi vake vakati kwaari: Munoda kuti tiende kupi kunogadzira pamungadya paseka?
\v 13 Akatuma vadzidzi vake vaviri, akati kwavari: Endai muguta, ipapo muchasangana nomunhu akatakura chirongo chemvura; mumutevere.
\v 14 Paanenge angopinda, muti kumwene weimba: Mudzidzisi wati: Imba yangu yavaeni iripiko, mandingadyira paseka navadzidzi vangu?
\v 15 Zvino iye amene uchakutaridzai imba huru yokumusoro, yakarongedzwa, yakagadzirwa; mutigadzirirepo.
\v 16 Vadzidzi vake vakabuda, vakasvika muguta, vakandowana sezvaakanga avavudza; vakagadzira paseka.
\v 17 Ava madekwana, akavuya navanegumi navaviri.
\v 18 Zvino vakati vakagara pakudya, Jesu akati: Zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwamuri: Mumwe wenyu uri pakudya neni uchandipandukira.
\v 19 Ipapo vakatanga kuva neshungu, mumwe nomumwe akati kwaari: Ndini here?
\v 20 Asi wakavapindura akati kwavari: Mumwe wavanegumi navaviri, unoisa ruvoko neni mundiro.
\v 21 Mwanakomana womunhu unoenda zvirokwazvo, sezvakanyorwa pamusoro pake; asi unenhamo munhu uyo, Mwanakomana womunhu waanopandukirwa naye, kwaiva nani kumunhu uyu kana asina kuberekwa.
\v 22 Zvino vakati vachidya, Jesu akatora chingwa, akaropafadza, akamedura, ndokuvapa, achiti: Torai, ichi ndiwo muviri wangu.
\v 23 Akatora mukombe, akati avonga, akavapa, vakanwa vose pauri.
\v 24 Zvino akati kwavari: Ichi iropa rangu resungano itsva, rinodururirwa vazhinji.
\v 25 Zvirokwazvo, ndinoti kwamuri: Handichazonwizve zvibereko zvomuzambiringa, kusvikira zuva iro randichazonwa naro, zvava zvitsva, muvushe bwaMwari.
\v 26 Zvino vakati vaimba rwiyo, vakabuda, vakaenda kugomo reMiorivhi.
\s Jesu unovudza Petro kuti uchamuramba.
\p
\p
\v 27 Zvino Jesu wakati kwavari: Imi mose muchagumburwa neni vusiku bwuno, nokuti kwakanyorwa, \add kuchinzi\add*: Ndicharova mufudzi, namakwai achaparadzwa.
\v 28 Asi kana ndamutswa,ndichakutungamirirai Gariri.
\v 29 Zvino Petro akati kwaari: Kunyange vose vakagumburwa, asi ini kwete.
\v 30 Jesu akati kwaari: Zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwauri, kuti nhasi, vusiku bwuno, jongwe risati rarira kaviri, uchandiramba katatu.
\v 31 Asi iye wakareva nesimba, \add achiti\add*: Kunyange ndikafanira kufa nemi, handingatongokurambiyi ini. Navose vakadarovo
\s Jesu muGetsemani
\p
\v 32 Zvino vakasvika panzvimbo yainzi Getsemani, akati kuvadzidzi vake: Garai pano, ini ndichindonyengetera.
\v 33 Akatora pamwechete naye Petro naJakobho naJohwani, akatanga kuvhunduka kwazvo nokudumbirwa.
\v 34 Akati kwavari: Mweya wangu uneshungu kwazvo, kusvikira pakufa; garai pano murinde.
\v 35 Akapfuvura mberi zvishoma, akawira pasi, akanyengetera kuti kana zvichibvira, nguva ipfuvure kwaari.
\v 36 Zvino akati: Aba, Baba, zvose zvinobvira kwamuri, bvisai mukombe uyu kwandiri, asi ngakutongorega kuva kuda kwangu, asi kuda kwenyu..
\v 37 Zvino akasvika, akavawana vavata; akati kunaPetro: Simoni, uvete here? Wakanga usingagoni kurinda nguva imwe chete here?
\v 38 Rindai, munyengetere, kuti murege kupinda mukuidzwa; mweya unoda hawo, asi nyama hainesimba.
\v 39 Akaenda zve, akanyengetera achireva mashoko iwayo.
\v 40 Akaendazve, akavawana vavata, nokuti meso avo akanga abatwa nehope kwazvo; vakasaziva zvavangamupindura.
\v 41 Akavuyazve rwechitatu, akati kwavari: Chivatai henyu, muzorore; Zvaringana, nguva yasvika, Mwanakomana womunhu woiswa mumavoko avatadzi.
\v 42 Simukai, tiende; tarirai, wondiisa kwavari wava pedo.
\s Kusungwa kwaJesu.
\p
\v 43 Pakarepo, achataura, Judhasi, mumwe wavanegumi navaviri, akasvika, anavanhu vazhinji vakabata minondo netsvimbo, vachibva kuvapirisita vakuru navanyori navakuru.
\v 44 Zvino iye, wakamupandukira, wakanga avapa chiratidzo, achiti: Uyo wandinosveta ndiye, mumubate muende naye makamusunga zvakabata.
\v 45 Zvino wakati asvika, pakarepo akaswedera kwaari, akati: Mudzidzisi! Akamusveta zvikuru.
\v 46 Ipapo vakaisa mavoko kwaari, vakamubata.
\v 47 Zvino mumwe wavakanga vamirepo, wakavhomora munondo wake, akatema muranda womupirisita mukuru, akagura nzeve yake.
\v 48 Ipapo Jesu akapindura, akati kwavari: Mabuda kuzondibata neminondo netsvimbo, sendiri gororo here?
\v 49 Ndakanga ndinemi mazuva ose, ndichidzidzisa mutembere, mukarega kundibata, asi izvi zvaitwa, kuti Magwaro aitike.
\v 50 Ipapo vakamusiya vose, vakatiza.
\v 51 Zvino rimwe jaya rakamutevera, rakamonera mucheka werineni chete pamuviri rakashama, vakaribata;
\v 52 asi rakasiya mucheka, rikatiza rakashama.
\s Jesu pamberi pomupirisita mukuru navakuru.
\p
\v 53 Zvino vakabudisira Jesu kumupirisita mukuru; vapirisita vakuru vose navakuru navanyori vakavunganira kwaari.
\v 54 Petro akamutevera ari kure kusvikira paruvazhe rwomupirisita mukuru; akanga agere navatariri, achidziya moto.
\v 55 Zvino vapirisita vakuru namakurukota ose vakatsvaka chapupu pamusoro paJesu kuti vamuvuraye, asi vakashaiwa
\v 56 Nokuti vazhinji vaimupupurira nhema, asi kupupura kwavo kwakapesana.
\v 57 Vamwe vakasimuka, vakamupupurira nhema, vachiti:
\v 58 Isu takamunzwa isu achiti: Ndichaputsa tembere iyi; yakavakwa namavoko, uye namazuva matatu ndichavaka imwe, isina kuvakwa namavoko.
\v 59 Asi kupupura kwavo kwakapesana.
\v 60 Zvino mupirisita mukuru akasimuka pakati \add pavo\add*, akabvunza Jesu, achiti: Haupinduri chinhu here? Chinyi \add ichi\add* chavanokupomedzera?
\v 61 Asi iye wakaramba anyerere, akasapindura chinhu. Mupirisita mukuru akamubvunzazve, akati kwaari: Ndiwe Kristu, Mwanakomana wowakaropafadzwa here?
\v 62 Jesu akati: Ndini. Nemi muchavona Mwanakomana womunhu agere kurudyi rwesimba, achivuya namakore okudenga.
\v 63 Ipapo mupirisita mukuru akabvarura nguvo dzake, akati: Tichatsvakireiko zvimwe zvapupu?
\v 64 Manzwa kumhura kwake Mwari; munofungeiko? Ipapo vose vakamutongera kuti unofanira kufa.
\v 65 Vamwe vakatanga kumupfira mate, vakafukidza chiso chake, vakamurova netsiva, vachiti kwaari: Profita; navaranda vakamurova namavoko.
\s Kuramba kwaPetro.
\p
\v 66 Zvino Petro achiri panze paruvazhe, mumwe wavashandiri vomupirisita mukuru akasvika,
\v 67 zvino akavona Petro achizvidziyisa, akamutarira, akati: Newevo wakanga unaJesu weNazareta!
\v 68 Asi iye wakaramba, achiti: Handizivi kana kunzwisisa zvaunoreva; akabuda panze kuruvazhe rwapamberi, jongwe rikarira.
\v 69 Zvino murandakadzi akamuvonazve, akatanga kuti kunavakanga varipo, achiti: Uyu ndomumwe wavo!
\v 70 Asi iye wakaramba zve. Nguva duku yakati yapfuvura, vakanga vamirepo vakati zve kuna Petro: Zvirokwazvo, uri mumwe wavo, nokuti newe vo uri muGariri nokuti rurimi rwako runotenderana nazvo.
\v 71 Ipapo akatanga kutuka nokupika, achiti: Handimuzivi munhu uyu wamunoreva.
\v 72 Pakarepo jongwe rikarira rwechipiri; ipapo Petro akarangarira shoko rakanga rarebwa kwaari naJesu rokuti: Jongwe risati rarira kaviri, uchandiramba katatu. Zvino wakati achifunga izvozvo, akachema.
